velocity financial meet our team   michael james barnes with almost  years of experience in the origination and securitization of residential and commercial mortgages michael j barnes serves as president of velocity financial llc a scottsdalebased company that specializes in providing a variety of mortgage products to individuals and corporate entities as president mr barnes is responsible for the daytoday operation of velocity financial and supervision of the company’s staff he is in charge of product and new business development overseeing the applicant screening process market analysis state licensing procedures and regulations lender relations and closings and funding mortgage loans prior to opening velocity financial in august 06 barnes served as president of rg capital equity lending llc where he started a mortgage bank for rg capital investments prior to that he was vice president of spectrum financial group inc where he supervised  mortgage professionals while at spectrum financial michael proved to be a valuable asset to the company by tripling branch loan closings increasing the number of loan officers by 0 percent creating a cost plan that saved the company more than  annually and substantially increasing loan officer revenue without affecting the company’s profitability he has spoken internationally on mortgage finance administered realtor training classes and developed a number of programs that increased customer loyalty in 06 michael earned his certified mortgage planner cmp certified mortgage planning specialistcmps and certified mortgage advisor cma designations the cmps designation is held by less than  mortgage plannersloan officers in the state of arizona a member of the national mortgage lenders associations and the arizona mortgage lenders associations michael and his wife leslie reside in north phoenix with their sons chase and mj and their daughter alice  n th street suite scottsdale az phone 8fax 8  get started velocity financial llcph 8fax 8